-title 'About Unconfirmed Users'
-breadcrumb :about_unconfirmed_users

%p Unconfirmed users are registered users who have yet to be flagged with the helper or editor roles.

%p
  Things you can do before we confirm your account:
  %ul
    %li
      Add and edit
      =link_to 'Open Issues', issues_path
    %li Post comments
    %li Submit feedback
    %li
      Edit
      =link_to 'wiki pages', wiki_pages_path

%p
  Unconfirmed user are allowed a maximum of
  =User::UNCONFIRMED_USER_EDIT_LIMIT_COUNT
  edits per day.
